<template>
  
</template>

<script>
  import { mapState } from 'vuex';

  export default {
    name: 'CustomSetting',
    computed: {
      ...mapState({
        customizer: (state) => state.menu.customizer,
      }),
    },
    methods: {
      openCustomizerSetting(val) {
        this.$store.state.menu.customizer = val;
      },
    },
  };
</script>
